  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2534490/extras/8b28f278d32387f86c524b72c31dea6f.avif?t=1692020457\" width=500 height=90 /></span><br><strong>Welcome To Vexed Heroes!</strong><br><br><strong>Key Features Include:</strong><br>5 Unlockable unique Heroes.<br>Level Up system featuring skill path's.<br>Endless New Game Plus scaling.<br>Endless permanent stat bonus progression.<br>2 Stages to play on.<br>Fun cute art.<br>And lot's of Violence!<br><br>This was a passion Project I have been working on for a long while to learn how to make games.<br>I hope you Enjoy it as much as I enjoyed working on it, I cant wait to make more!",
